channel.title: Webclient "Could not find main class: client"
channel.description:
OK I made a webclinet, and it downloads the cache perfectly and runs perfectly on my computer. But its online and when anyone does it from there computer they get an error message saying "Could not find the main class: jframe". Iv done everything write because I go to my site and it downloads the cache, unpacks it, then starts the clinet succesfully. My site it http://www.skideria.com/tyler/Run.html Please help!!!
P.S: If this helps im using the HybridPvP V3 "webclient ready.rar", to make the client. With the Hybrid Pvp V3 source!
